				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: The Cost of a Bad Hire</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-04-08T17:16:38+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">April 8, 2014 1:16 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">April 8, 2014 1:16 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/04/08/today-in-small-business-the-cost-of-a-bad-hire/" data-title="Today in Small Business: The Cost of a Bad Hire" data-description="Legal pot is becoming a workplace issue. Ten tricks for getting paid faster. Is affiliate marketing right for your business?">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Home-buyer traffic in March <a href="//blogs.wsj.com/economics/2014/04/07/homebuyer-traffic-in-march-was-down-from-last-year/?">was down</a> from last year, and soaring housing costs are <a href="//blogs.wsj.com/economics/2014/04/04/soaring-housing-costs-driving-educated-people-from-big-cities/">driving educated people</a> from big cities.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Employees</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here&#8217;s what it costs to <a href="//www.fastcompany.com/3028628/work-smart/infographic-how-much-a-bad-hire-will-actually-cost-you?partner=rss#2">make a bad hire</a>.</p>
